targets.query: SELECT "job", "build_url", "release", "build_type", "branch", "hardware_revision", "hardware_variant", "build", "job_timestamp" FROM "job_duration" WHERE ("hardware_revision" =~ /^$hardware_revision$/) AND ("job" =~ /^$job_name$/) AND $timeFilter

SELECT "value" 
FROM "app_start_time_value" 
WHERE ("app"  =~ /^$Application$/) AND "type_of_boot" = 'COLD' AND ("job" =~ /^$job_name$/) AND ("build" =~ /^$build_id$/) AND ("hardware_revision" =~ /^$hardware_revision$/) AND $timeFilter
